::Ramulus::

Ramulus nods, entering the shuttle. He presses a button at a console, the 
design familiar to him, and activates the comm.

"Shuttle to Ark," he says into a mike, "Are we clear for liftoff?"

"Yeah, go ahead," Striker's voice replies.

Ramulus turns to Brix. "All clear."
